20:30.000 --> 20:33.000
No video exists of the one-time-only performance

20:33.000 --> 20:35.000
of  The Adventures
of Black Jesus.

20:36.000 --> 20:39.000
Just as well. I hate looking at my old work.

20:45.000 --> 20:46.000
Ahhh!

20:48.000 --> 20:51.000
I heard you work for Santa.

20:51.000 --> 20:52.000
I got a message for him.

20:53.000 --> 20:55.000
Tell him Riley said,

20:55.000 --> 20:58.000
I'll be waiting for his ass
next Christmas.

